    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individue Trinitatis. <persName ref="#people/21"
                            key="#Emperor/king">Berengarius</persName> divina favente clementia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Noverit omnium fidelium sancte Dei Eclesie
                        nostrorumque presentium scilicet ac futurorum [industria], <persName
                            ref="#people/155" key="#Queen">Berchtilam</persName> dilectissimam <rs
                            key="#marriage">coniugem</rs> nostrique [regni]
                        consortem nec non et <persName key="#fidelisOf">Odonem</persName> illustrem
                        virum dilectumque <rs key="#fidelisOf">fidelem</rs> nostrum suppliciter
                        nostram exorasse clementiam, quatenus quondam <rs
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Redistributive #Gift">curtem</rs> que
                        nominatur <geogName ref="#estates/152"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/267" key="#Fiscal_property"
                                >Runco</placeName></geogName> pertinentem de <rs key="#Comitatus"
                            >comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName ref="#estates/151" key="#Comitatus"><placeName ref="#places/262"
                                key="#Cities">Laudensi</placeName></geogName>, sitam in eodem
                        comitatu, adiacentem iuxta <rs key="#Rivers">fluvium</rs> qui dicitur
                        Brembio non longe a <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio</rs> Lambro, cum omnibus
                        adiacentiis et pertinentiis suis, nec non et <persName
                            key="#Slave #Royal_slave">Petrus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Slave_labour #Slave #Royal_slave">servus</rs> eiusdem comitatus,
                        qui in ipsa curte habitare videtur, filium quondam <persName key="#Slave"
                            >Landoni</persName> de <placeName key="#Villages/settlements #Vici">vico
                            Antoniano</placeName> cum <rs
                            key="#Slave #Royal_slave #marriage">uxore</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Slave #Royal_slave #sonOf">filiis</rs> ac <rs
                            key="#Slave #Royal_slave #daughterOf">filiabus</rs> suis, seu quicquid
                        ad comitatum Laudensem pertinet de <rs key="#Local_markets">mercato</rs>
                        quod dicitur de <placeName ref="#places/263"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Vici #Local_markets"
                            >Vicomercatum</placeName> cum <rs key="#Teloneum">teloneo</rs> vel censu
                        aut redibitionibus cum omni curatura sua, et terram que ad eundem <rs
                            key="#Local_markets">mercatum</rs> aliquo modo pertinet simul cum
                        mansionibus et omnibus ad se pertinentibus <persName ref="#people/188"
                            key="#Marquis/duke #Count">Grimaldo</persName> glorioso <rs key="#Count"
                            >comiti</rs>
                        <rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">iure proprietario</rs> concedere
                        dignaremur. Quorum precibus aclinati, prenominatam cortem Runcum cum toto
                            <rs key="#Domuscultae">domo cultili</rs> sui omnibusque <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">masseritiis</rs> atque familiis
                        utriusque sexus, servis et ancillis, aldionibus et aldianis, casis
                        videlicet, terris, vineis, campis, pratis, silvis, pascuis, salectis,
                        sationibus, aquis aquarumque decursibus, <rs key="#Mills">molendinis</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs>, una cum prenominato Petro
                        servus eiusdem comitatus, qui ibidem habitare videtur, seu quicquid ad
                        eundem comitatum pertinere dinoscitur de <rs key="#Local_markets"
                            >mercato</rs> quod dicitur de Vicomercato cum <rs key="#Teloneum"
                            >teloneo</rs>, <rs key="#Districtio">districtionibus</rs>,
                        reddibitionibus atque censu seu cum omni curatura sua, et terra ac
                        mansionibus exinde iuste et legaliter pertinentibus iam dicto Grimaldo
                        comiti in integrum presenti auctoritate concedimus et largimur, et de nostra
                        potestate in suam potestatem transfundimus atque donamus ad abendum,
                        tenendum [â€¦]</ab>
